    <title>Calculus (C2,C3,C4,NM,FP2)</title>
<p>The calculator allows you to find the differential (rate of change) and integral
 (the area between the curve and the x-axis) of most functions.</p>
<p> We may find the differential of polynomials:</p>
<code>
differentiate (3x^3 - 4.5x^2 + 6x - 2)
   = 9x^2 - 9x + 6
</code>
